\begin_layout Standard
As mentioned above DASH7 is uses an open source protocol used by Wizzimote.
 It typically used for wireless sensor networks.
 Compared to other technologies like ZigBee, devices that use DASH7 has
 a wider range spanning up to 2 kilometers which is optimal for an outdoor
 project.
 It is also flexible in such a way that it can also propagate its signal
 for indoors, because DASH7 can penetrate thick walls easily unlike Wifi
 and Bluetooth 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
